---
title: "Deal Stage Progress Notification"
---
The **Deal Stage Progress Notification** ensures effective communication by sending automated emails to both the contact and the deal owner whenever a deal stage is changed. By automating notifications, the flow enhances transparency, fosters collaboration, and saves valuable time.

### Business Type

This flow is best suited for **B2B, SaaS,** and **service-based industries** focused on improving communication and keeping all stakeholders informed about deal progress.

### Template Type

Here we have used the Campaign Templates to send Emails to contacts and Send Internal Email to the owner of the Deal.

### Use Case

When a deal is moved to any stage, this flow automatically notifies both the contact and the deal owner via email, ensuring everyone is on the same page about the deal's progress.

### Key Features of the Flow **Automatic Trigger**:

Activates whenever a deal stage is updated to "New."**Dual Notifications**:
Sends automated emails to both the contact and the deal owner for improved transparency.

- **Time-Saving Automation**:
Eliminates the need for manual follow-ups by automating notification emails.

###**Steps Used in Creating the Flow** Please [click here](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/36752706603929-How-to-Create-New-Smart-Flow) to learn how to create a new Smart Flow or access the Flow Templates.

- **Record Updated [Trigger](#key-features-of-the-flow-automatic-trigger):**- **Description:** This flow is automatically triggered when a record, such as a deal stage, is updated to a value like "Contacted."

- **Practical Use-Case:** You can automate follow-up actions, such as notifying the contact or updating internal teams about the progress whenever there is an update in the Record.

- **Send Flow Email [Action](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38138164432409):**- **Description:** This action sends an automated email to the contact, providing updates or relevant information based on the deal's progress.

- **Practical Use-Case:** Automatically send a personalized email to the record ensuring they stay informed without manual intervention or you can send campaigns to have better engagements.

- **Send Internal Email [Action](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/38138259670809):**- **Description:** This action sends an internal notification email to team members, such as the deal owner, to keep them updated on key changes.

- **Practical Use-Case:** Notify the owner or teammates via email whenever some actions are performed, ensuring they are promptly informed and can take necessary actions.

### Breakup of Items Used in the Flow** Trigger:**Record Updated:** When the Record is updated the flow will triggered.

- **Actions:**Send Flow Email **: An automated email is sent to the contact as a part of the flow.

- ** Send Internal Email **: A notification email is sent internally to the deal owner.

### Benefits **Enhanced Transparency**: Keeps both clients and internal teams informed, fostering trust and clarity.

- **Stronger Collaboration**: Ensures all stakeholders have real-time updates for seamless coordination.

- **Time Efficiency**: Reduces manual workload with automated notifications, letting teams focus on higher-value tasks.

- The **Automated Notifications on Deal Stage Change** Smart Flow is a perfect solution for businesses seeking to improve communication, boost team collaboration, and streamline their deal management processes. Ensuring timely updates drives operational efficiency and builds trust with clients.
